overview:
The Company:

Elia Web Designs creates web presence solutions for businesses which are both in need of visibility and client growth. Our focus is our client’s happiness and to that end we create designs that are pleasing to our clients as well as providing that web face that keeps their customers flowing in - from new to repeat customers.

Our Services include: Web design and website creation. Web hosting services via Go daddy SEO work - which includes site optimization. URL submissions - Link creations etc. This service ensures that you are visible and accessible on all search engines. Local, National and International marketing - this services ensures that you are listed in all local directories, national, international. Managing your web marketing and ads distribution. In addition to adding marketing themes that ensure visibility of your ad. We tailor this to your business needs so you can choose one, two or all the three options - Local, National or International.

Our prices are not only reasonable but are customized by the client’s needs.

Our turn over is a few days - we promise your site will be up and running in a few days or your money back.
